variable number equal 1
variable ofreq  equal 1000
variable efreq  equal 1000
variable T      equal 0.1
variable rhos   equal 0.2

units lj

dimension 3

newton on

boundary  p p p

atom_style hybrid bond ellipsoid oxdna
